{"tid":530533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄士兵生火加熱罐頭　不慎燒毀392萬元裝甲車","createTime":"2018-01-16T00:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T07:42:36.000Z","uid":53379,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"00797b0061b497b27e1c5bac2b6e990d5822f58c","tid":530533,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">俄士兵生火加熱罐頭　不慎燒毀392萬元裝甲車</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180115/s00005/bcaeb892e37f0aa63965c060676546c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180115%2Fs00005%2Fbcaeb892e37f0aa63965c060676546c1.jpg&h=124424e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯人經常被網民稱為「戰鬥民族」，不過似乎並非每一個俄羅斯人都善戰。去年5月在克里米亞俄軍駐地，一名士兵生火加熱食罐頭食品時，不慎燒毀了一輛價值36.5萬英鎊(約392萬港元)的裝甲車，有關影片近日流出。<br />\n<br />\n片段中顯示，士兵梅里芝尼克夫（Semen Merezhnikov）在燒毀裝甲車後，被長官責罵，他解釋自己在裝甲車旁挖了一個坑，生火煮食，而在身後可見，裝甲車正在燃燒。禍不單行，梅里芝尼克夫手上拿著的手榴彈槍同樣著火，長官立即喝令他將火撲熄。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，裝甲車上覆蓋迷彩網和乾草，十分易燃。這件事發生在去年5月，梅里芝尼克夫已被處分，他不需賠償裝甲車的價錢，但需要勞動、清洗厠所和減少睡眠6個月。<br />\n<br />\n(每日郵報/聯合新聞網/鏡報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bf5pet9Lf-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBf5pet9Lf-Y&d=hhXIQQLhWnbAiN3mV1lGMQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=544c27fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bf5pet9Lf-Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180115/s00005/1516010584566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180115%2Fs00005%2F1516010584566&d=hhXIQQLhWnbAiN3mV1lGMQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f353c1e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180115%2Fs00005%2F1516010584566&h=575fe283\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180115/s00005/1516010584566</a>"},{"pid":"5b5